# BioAnalytiX Website — Environment Variables (example)
#
# Copy this file to `.env.local` for local development, or configure these
# values in the Vercel Project Settings → Environment Variables for deploys.
#
# ALL variables below are SERVER-ONLY. They are read exclusively inside Next.js
# Server Actions (app/actions/*) and the server-side helpers (lib/email.ts,
# lib/submissions-store.ts, lib/rate-limit.ts). They are NOT prefixed with
# NEXT_PUBLIC_ and are therefore never inlined into the client bundle.
# (Requirements 15.4, 6.5)
#
# Do NOT commit real secrets. This file documents variable names only.

# --- Contact form → email via Resend (app/actions/submit-contact.ts) --------

# Required. Resend API key (https://resend.com). Contact submissions are emailed
# to the inbox below. If unset, the contact action returns a generic delivery
# failure and retains the visitor's input (Requirement 15.5).
RESEND_API_KEY=

# Optional. Recipient inbox for contact submissions. Default: info@bioanalytix.info
CONTACT_TO_EMAIL=info@bioanalytix.info

# Optional. Verified sender address (must be on a Resend-verified domain, e.g.
# the verified bioanalytix.info domain). Default: noreply@bioanalytix.info
CONTACT_FROM_EMAIL=BioAnalytiX Website <noreply@bioanalytix.info>

# --- Beta / careers / collaboration requests → private Google Sheet ----------
# (app/actions/submit-beta.ts, lib/submissions-store.ts)
#
# Applications from the shared form (/beta, /careers, /data-partner) are appended
# as rows to a PRIVATE Google Sheet via a Google Cloud service account. Share the
# sheet with the service-account email as an Editor; it stays private otherwise.
# If these are unset, the action returns a generic failure and retains the
# applicant's input (Requirement 15.5).

# Required. The target spreadsheet id (the long token in the sheet URL between
# /d/ and /edit).
GOOGLE_SHEETS_SPREADSHEET_ID=

# Required. The service-account email (…@….iam.gserviceaccount.com). The sheet
# must be shared with this address as an Editor.
GOOGLE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_EMAIL=

# Required. The service-account private key. Newlines may be stored escaped as
# \n (they are normalized at runtime). Wrap the whole value in quotes.
GOOGLE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_PRIVATE_KEY="-----BEGIN PRIVATE KEY-----\n...\n-----END PRIVATE KEY-----\n"

# Optional. Append range / tab name. Default: Submissions!A:G
GOOGLE_SHEETS_RANGE=Submissions!A:G

# --- Rate limiting (lib/rate-limit.ts) --------------------------------------
# Both are optional. Out-of-range values are clamped to safe defaults.

# Optional. Rolling window length in seconds. Clamped to 1–3600. Default: 60.
RATE_LIMIT_WINDOW_SECONDS=60

# Optional. Maximum submissions allowed per window. Clamped to 1–1000. Default: 5.
RATE_LIMIT_MAX_SUBMISSIONS=5
